data.description: Welcome Home to Augusta Woods! This 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home is situated in a quiet community, overlooking Walter Hall Golf Course. The open concept main floor features a nice kitchen with stainless steel appliances, walk-in pantry, and breakfast bar connecting the dining room. The cozy living room with gas fireplace and 1/2 bath completes the main floor. Upstairs is where you'll find the 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. The primary bedroom has a vaulted ceiling and a 5 piece ensuite bathroom. The backyard has a patio with a view of the greens and a side yard to enjoy relaxing morning coffee or summer BBQ's. This charming neighborhood is conveniently located near Boeing, Paine Field, parks, Mukilteo Ferry Terminal, shopping and more!
